name: Tsuki Inu (TKINU)
description: $TKINU is a 100% decentralized peer-to-peer digital currency fully owned by its fun, ambitious community. We aim to build the best cryptocurrency community the world has yet to see. 2% of every transaction (buy/sell) is re-distributed to $TKINU holders. If you own own $TKINU, you can sit back and watch your balance grow! We have locked away Liquidity & sent 50% of total supply to a burn address – no chance of a Vitalik rug! We have also conducted a security audit for our contract, to secure the community’s trust.
